entries.do_humans: Hey, do your impression of those human fellas.
entries.alright_humans: So you want to see what humans are like, eh? Well just you watch this...it is uncanny.
entries.i_am_human: Hey look at me. I am human. I am so pretty. This lava is too hot for my tender pink skin. Oooo, it is a scary blistmok...help me...help me.
entries.i_love_that: It is funny because it is true.
entries.wookiee_smell: No way! Those walking furballs smell something fierce.
entries.offworlders: Hey, guys. Watch this. I am going to do all those treasure hunters out in those ruins thinking they are going to get rich. Silly off-worlders...there are more credits floating in the lava pools than they will ever find in those dumb ruins.
entries.do_rodian: I bet you can't do a Rodian.
entries.okay_rodian: Hmmmmm...rodian eh? That could be a tough one...
entries.i_am_rodian: Hey everyone, I am Rodian.  Look at me with my skinny green legs and my flappy little lips. I am a scary bounty hunter...OoooOOooO.
entries.rodian_yellow: Rodians are all yella...well green anyways. They are all supposed to be scary but how can you be scary with those weird things sticking out of your head?
